        },
        {
            "chapter": 100,
            "verse": 5,
            "text": "攻入敵圍的馬隊盟誓"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 100,
            "verse": 6,
            "text": "人對于主, 確是孤負的。"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 100,
            "verse": 7,
